content.title: PostBeyond Outreach - Feature Request
content.visibleText:
Hi George Dita,
I have seen your work at PostBeyond and I am directly sharing that we have an idea on developing and enhancing our platform to be inclusive of more than features. Currently, we are yet to test and implement these features, and we would like to have your feedback.
With our team of tech developers, if you are interested and if it would be valuable to you, we at PostBeyond are working on right now.
One of the key areas we believe PostBeyond would excel in is just having a better roadmap for this feature.
Best regards,
Danny Stone
Product Manager, PostBeyond
